    "updated_at": "2016-04-19T23:48:37Z",
    "body": "The `setXxxxable` methods are the right way to go.\n\nHowever implementing events like `beforemaximize` are not possible on many platforms, it is a platform limitation that we can not work around in Electron.\n"
